Class WebSocketFrame.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • universum.studios.websocket.adapter.WebSocketFrame.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    WebSocketFrame

    public static final class WebSocketFrame.Builder
extends Object
    Builder that may be used to create instances of WebSocketFrame with a desired data.

    Required parameters

    Parameters specified below are required in order to create a new instance of WebSocketFrame via build() successfully.
